    "What this leaves out is the question of how to regulate or control for non-manipulative AI (both of which can be approached from a design perspective, of course).",
    "Note also that I will not discuss how do balance the goal of non-manipulation with other values.",
    "An important aspect of design approaches to values in technology is that they will have to deal with conflicting values van de Poel (2015).",
